text: Milky Way is a chocolate bar. It was made in 1923. It is covered in chocolate and caramel. It is best known for being made by Mars, Incorporated and for being ranked 6 out of 25 in the top chocolate bars in the United States. March 12th is Milky Way Day. == References == Category:Chocolate bars Category:Mars, Incorporated
title: Milky Way (chocolate bar)
